Package genetic

Package containing the Genetic Algorithm and its tools to generate RedCode programs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlgoGen  
    CellToFile
    Class to turn given program under the form of a List of Cells to a File with given name.
    Duel
    Object used as Thread by the Pool to run duels between to programs.
    Elitism
    Object used as a for elitisme method of selection.
    Mixer
    Object used to mix programs together.
    Mutator
    Object used to mutate given programs.
    PairProgs
    Object representing a task for the thread and holding the results of its evaluation.
    Pool  
    Selector
    Abstract Object containing method to select programs for the AlgoGen.
    Util
    Class containing static usefull methods for the AlgoGen.
    Wheel
    Object used as a for wheel method of selection.
